<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Message Received</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6, #2563eb);
      color: white;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
    }
    .logo {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .content {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 40px 30px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-top: none;
      border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
    }
    .greeting {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #111827;
    }
    .message {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 20px;
      border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .cta {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #3b82f6;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .social {
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .social a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 0 10px;
      color: #3b82f6;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <div class="logo">Jahongir Travel</div>
    <p>Discover the Beauty of Uzbekistan</p>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <div class="greeting">
      Hi {{name}},
    </div>

    <p>Thank you for contacting Jahongir Travel! We've received your message and our team will get back to you within 24 hours.</p>

    <div class="message">
      <p><strong>ðŸ“Œ What's Next?</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Our team is reviewing your inquiry</li>
        <li>We'll respond to <strong>{{email}}</strong> shortly</li>
        <li>In the meantime, explore our amazing tours</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="cta">
      <a href="https://jahongir-travel.uz/tours" class="button">
        Browse Our Tours
      </a>
    </div>

    <p>If you have any urgent questions, feel free to call us at +998 XX XXX XX XX.</p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p><strong>Jahongir Travel</strong><br>
      Your Gateway to Uzbekistan</p>

      <div class="social">
        <a href="#">Facebook</a> |
        <a href="#">Instagram</a> |
        <a href="#">Telegram</a>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px;">
        This email was sent to {{email}}. You're receiving this because you contacted us through our website.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
